body:
# jslab
JS Lab
========

Installation
========
1. Install npm
1. npm install -g gulp phantomjs karma
1. npm install

Running the Project
========
1. Run `gulp server` in your project root directory
1. Open your browser to [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080)


Use gulp to build, test, etc. the app.
